-- Hungary’s Orban Says He’ll Rebut ‘Lies’ at European Parliament
-- B y   A n d r a s   G e r g e l y
-- 2012-01-17T07:57:08Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-01-17/hungary-s-orban-says-he-ll-rebut-lies-at-european-parliament.html
Hungarian Prime Minister  Viktor Orban  has asked to speak at the European Parliament tomorrow to
defend the country against “lies and groundless accusations,”
his spokesman  Peter Szijjarto  said in a statement late
yesterday.  To contact the reporter on this story:
